":"内蒙古","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":349242,"user_name":"沈子砚","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2049011,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E00BE02AF51F11","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/1znsUF88YEepJS9I58GGJict9NYTRybkz993KlPpvnC0sTibm3d6bWLIyhcETsYrVDPiakiaextmrXbnFkIsL7EfRQ/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1655825941,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":127289,"content":"我认为组织上不做去中心化其实很难做到行为和决策的去中心化， 就像历史上的封建国家最终都没有发展出民主的决策一样。  \n","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2574960,"ctime":1656310860,"ip_address":"","comment_id":349242,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100099801,"comment_content":"东白老师好，请问去中心化的团队是一个虚拟团队吗？或者说去中心化是一种做事的指导思想，因为不一定组织上能做到去中心化，能做到的也是为一些明星项目单独成立项目组或者虚拟团队，不知我的理解对不对？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":350450,"user_name":"徐李","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1213325,"ip_address":"","ucode":"41550F6CA1E112","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/83/8d/03cac826.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1656920794,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100099801,"comment_content":"我特别认可的一点在于，架构师需要一个决策环境，需要面临风险的环境，这样在风险环境下的决策才能不断提高自己的价值思维能力，风险决策能力，敢于决断的能力；以此不断往复，不断正反馈，让自己的能力不断提升。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":349263,"user_name":"罗均","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2859088,"ip_address":"","ucode":"AA8F5D6B13D3E6","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/2b/a0/50/390187f3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1655857226,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":127293,"content":"去“我执” 的理解非常深刻， 赞！ ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2574960,"ctime":1656311114,"ip_address":"","comment_id":349263,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100099801,"comment_content":"感谢东白老师的课程！\n\n老师这节课的“去中心化思想”论述，更具体地验证了Peter Drucker于四五十年前预计的knowledge workers will take the much more responsibilities的企业现象。从以前的“老板拍板制”到今日的“数据驱动制”，时代以及发生了巨大的变化。\n\n在此模块导读课的思考题中，学生关于“思考质量”的留言是：坚信古今圣贤提倡的“无我之心”，私欲越少思考质量越高。\n\n今日学习此课后的思考，就更清晰了，就是对自己要“无我”，对待teammates要“无人”，对待用户与客户要“无众生”，对待产品要“无寿者”。去除“我执”，不断地以更全面更清晰的视角重新审视自己，teammates，用户与顾客，以及产品。","like_count":11,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2574960,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/27/4a/70/c16655c6.jpg","nickname":"郭东白～Dongbai","note":"","ucode":"A91E32F405A5A0","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":577726,"discussion_content":"去“我执” 的理解非常深刻， 赞！ ","likes_number":2,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1656311114,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1033219,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/c4/03/f753fda7.jpg","nickname":"JianXu","note":"","ucode":"2A61BDBB573BDC","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":581507,"discussion_content":"这里有佛家的理念了","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1658820356,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":349288,"user_name":"彭彭😄","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2854829,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C6E4EC410E52F6","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/2b/8f/ad/c3aa2da3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1655868521,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":127295,"content":"“甘为鱼肉” 这种牺牲精神从公司角度讲是对的。 但是从个人角度讲有不是最优， 违反人性。\n\n我总是认为应该是公司和个人形成一个相互促进的正循环才行， 牺牲任何一方都很难最大化生存。  ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2574960,"ctime":1656311418,"ip_address":"","comment_id":349288,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":3,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100099801,"comment_content":"在一个新的环境，为了巩固自己的架构师地位，会不惜让自己成为单点，提升自己的不可替代性。\n当解决生存问题之后，再去寻求更进一步的成长，这时可以采取去中心化思维。\n不过从个人角度讲，确实没有采用去中心化的动力。东白老师给的理由是：“管理者视角觉得这种不可取”，个人感觉说服力不够强。从公司角度讲是不愿意让任何一个人不可替代。去中心化思维，意味着我要自断臂膀，让我可以被随时取代，有种我甘为鱼肉的感觉。","like_count":5,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2574960,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/27/4a/70/c16655c6.jpg","nickname":"郭东白～Dongbai","note":"","ucode":"A91E32F405A5A0","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":577726,"discussion_content":"去“我执” 的理解非常深刻， 赞！ ","likes_number":2,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1656311114,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1033219,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/c4/03/f753fda7.jpg","nickname":"JianXu","note":"","ucode":"2A61BDBB573BDC","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":581507,"discussion_content":"这里有佛家的理念了","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1658820356,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":349162,"user_name":"spark","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1116667,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2F128E884F400F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/09/fb/52a662b2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1655778317,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":127294,"content":"“提出问题的能力”\n“创造性思维”\n都非常好， 多谢建议！ ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2574960,"ctime":1656311214,"ip_address":"","comment_id":349162,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":4,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100099801,"comment_content":"郭老师，takeaway~~~找不到合适的工作，逼得思考两个问题，a.如何正确的技术决策，打造个人技术基因，毕竟时间和精力有限。b.如何学会生存，学了技术也不一定能找到合适工作，或者最大化生存能力~~~\n这篇专栏有一个前置条件或者问题，提出问题的能力，不是解决一个别人定义好的问题。如何提出问题？最笨的办法就是结构化自己的思考，价值思维、实证思维、去中心化思维、成长思维，通过这些思维输出的内容就是价值创造、规律、模型、场景~~~\n补充一点，架构师应该训练创造性思维，创造性思维关心的外部世界，关心如何改变世界。成长性思维是硬伤，说明能力不行，没底气，不读个博士，预测到死都是成长性思维~~~","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2574960,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/27/4a/70/c16655c6.jpg","nickname":"郭东白～Dongbai","note":"","ucode":"A91E32F405A5A0","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":577727,"discussion_content":"“提出问题的能力”\n“创造性思维”\n都非常好， 多谢建议！ ","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1656311214,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1031970,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/bf/22/26530e66.jpg","nickname":"趁早","note":"","ucode":"949FB3AA250D80","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":585371,"discussion_content":"我总觉得你每次的评论有点乱七八糟，不知道你在说啥，想说啥。核心观点也没表达出来","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1661501587,"is_liked":false,"can_dele